  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2986340/extras/c56d9ec8b2c757c54fc1b2b311a06cb6.avif?t=1757347750\" width=620 height=202 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Embark on a hilarious and chaotic adventure in <strong>Flood</strong>, the ultimate battle royale experience in unpredictable waters! Dive into a world where every sailor's dreamboat is a wonky, wobbly vessel crafted from scrap. Compete against friends and foes alike as you try to stay afloat and and engage in epic battles to be the last one standing!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Battle Royale</strong> multiplayer </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play with friends or public lobbies </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Choos from a wide varaity of parts to build the superia vessel</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Up to <strong>8 Players</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Physics-based chaos</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Colorful, crazy design</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Unlockable</strong> outfits</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fight scary <strong>monsters</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Lots of fun moments guaranteed!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Get your hands on <strong>Flood</strong> now and join in on the chaos!</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2986340/extras/c56d9ec8b2c757c54fc1b2b311a06cb6.avif?t=1757347750\" width=620 height=202 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Embark on a hilarious and chaotic adventure in <strong>Flood</strong>, the ultimate battle royale experience in unpredictable waters! Dive into a world where every sailor's dreamboat is a wonky, wobbly vessel crafted from scrap. Compete against friends and foes alike as you try to stay afloat and and engage in epic battles to be the last one standing!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Battle Royale</strong> multiplayer </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play with friends or public lobbies </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Choos from a wide varaity of parts to build the superia vessel</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Up to <strong>8 Players</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Physics-based chaos</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Colorful, crazy design</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Unlockable</strong> outfits</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fight scary <strong>monsters</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Lots of fun moments guaranteed!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Get your hands on <strong>Flood</strong> now and join in on the chaos!</p>",
